# Files/dirs to copy from the main checkout into a fresh git worktree.
# Worktrees start with only git-tracked files; this covers gitignored-but-useful outputs.
# Keep this small — heavy build caches (target/, app/build/) are intentionally NOT here:
# they're shared across worktrees via sccache (Cargo) + the Gradle build cache, not copied.
# Gitignore-style: one glob per line, # comments, blank-line grouping.

# App + web icons — regenerated by `just _gen-icons` (scripts/gen-icons.sh) only when
# assets/app-icon.png is newer; copying the built outputs lets that check skip regeneration.
src-tauri/icons/
public/icon-*.png
src-tauri/gen/android/app/src/main/res/mipmap-*/
src-tauri/gen/android/app/src/main/res/values/ic_launcher_background.xml
